WEBVTT

00:03:28.311 --> 00:03:33.527
and one girl fell in love
with her smile for the first time.

00:03:33.551 --> 00:03:36.687
At the end of the class,
I got a note that read

00:03:36.711 --> 00:03:40.167
"I always thought my smile
did not look good on me,

00:03:40.191 --> 00:03:42.647
but today I realized

00:03:42.671 --> 00:03:45.647
it really does suit me!"

00:03:45.671 --> 00:03:47.527
Be it these girls from Punjab,

00:03:47.551 --> 00:03:51.927
or children coping with the fear
of Taliban in Afghanistan,

00:03:51.951 --> 00:03:56.003
earthquake survivors picking
up the threads of life in Nepal,

00:03:56.836 --> 00:03:59.927
women stuck in the flesh trade,

00:03:59.951 --> 00:04:02.767
brave Indian soldiers,